agenda_items.title:
AGENDA 
CITY COUNCIL MEETING
MONDAY, JUNE 19, 2023
ORDER OF BUSINESS

The Special Called City Council meeting will be held by videoconference and in the Council Chambers, 6th Floor at City Hall.    

The public is encouraged to attend the meeting virtually; however, City Hall is available for those wishing to attend the meeting in person following all current pandemic-related public health protocols. 

The following videoconference link is available to the public to listen to the meeting and Public Affairs and Outreach will also stream the City Council meeting on Spectrum Cable Channel 16 and bit.ly/cityofdallastv: https://dallascityhall.webex.com/dallascityhall/j.php?MTID=m227e5ac2a0929ce21e4bd2e4b 71462fd

Receive the report of the Ad Hoc City Council Canvassing Committee and adopt a resolution and order accepting the canvassing committee's report declaring the results of the June 10, 2023 runoff election for members of the city council Financing: No cost consideration to the City
